{"tid":693654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實習總真心勁","createTime":"2018-06-07T15:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T00:46:37.000Z","uid":143372,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c95ef2e5a6f45949955311e1d4f2089e8d660b","tid":693654,"uid":143372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"自明清以來 韓國一直都係中國藩屬 <br />\n就算晚清國勢幾弱 一路都冇失去朝鮮半島話語權 <br />\n當然 之後係日本殖民時期 <br />\n但二戰一完 中國基本上至少立刻維持返半個朝鮮嘅話語權 <br />\n五六百年來 二戰後七八十年其本上中國都可以對朝鮮半島嘅政權有巨大影響力<br />\n<br />\n習總做左五年就可以玩到北韓冇撚左 成個朝鮮半島俾左人 <br />\n真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640a48024a710f01ad88a6fd1eddd322d23eca85","tid":693654,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d81c0a344f5eaeb954242a8c2bd8a9342eb586c","tid":693654,"uid":6030,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"下個到台灣獨立"},{"pid":"349844eba9c4c54193b5dd42ce948cac2ab33381","tid":693654,"uid":57835,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:54:42.000Z","msg":"咁勁你幫佢含撚啦"},{"pid":"2cae04cb5d4e87d356b189397b53e5c877560cd3","tid":693654,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d81c0a344f5eaeb954242a8c2bd8a9342eb586c","tid":693654,"uid":6030,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"下個到台灣獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /